'aK-UrYQ ZKYThY LBBY V'aUrChTSh BNQYVN KPhY.
V'aHY NGV'y KL-HYVM VThVKChThY LBQUrYM.
'aM-'aMUrThY 'aSPhUrH KMV HNH DVUr BNYK BGDThY.
V'aChShBH LD'yTh Z'aTh 'yML HY'a B'yYNY.
